display grid show data in a tablular form.
=> apply in parent element

list of property which is only effected while apply grid.

1. grid-template-rows (parent)
2. grid-template-columns (parent)

3. grid-row-start (child)
4. grid-row-end (child)
5. grid-row (child)

6. grid-column-start (child)
7. grid-column-end (child)
8. grid-column (child)

9. row-gap (parent)
10. column-gap (parent)
11. gap (parent)

12. justify-content (parent)
13. justify-items (parent)
14. justify-self (child)

15. align-content (parent)
16. align-items (parent)
17. align-self (child)

18. grid-area (child)
19. grid-template-areas (parent)

20. grid-auto-flow (parent)
21. grid-auto-rows (parent)
22. grid-auto-columns (parent)